; Regression test for issue #554
; Balance assertions should work correctly across multiple ledger files.
; The assertion in the second file (A = $2) must see the $1 balance
; accumulated from the first file.

test -f $sourcepath/test/regress/554a.dat -f $sourcepath/test/regress/554b.dat bal -> 0
                  $2  A
                 $-2  B
--------------------
                   0
end test
